            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
            <a href="/about" class="px-5 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
              Learn More About Us
            </a>
            <a href="https://liwox.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="px-5 py-3 bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
              Visit LiwoxDotNet
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-6">
            Why UK Homeowners Choose Us
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold">UK</span>
